Class Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • project3.Person
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Person>

    public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Person>
    Project #3 CS 2334, Section 010 Feb 18, 2015

    An object that contains data about a person, such as a first name, a last name, and a birthdate. Middle names are optional.

    Version:
    1.0
